  -- A variant of K-subst for _‚ä¢_‚áí*_‚à∑_.

opaque

  -- A variant of J-subst for _‚ä¢_‚áí*_‚à∑_.

  J-subst* :

  -- Validity of the J Œ≤ rule.

  J-Œ≤·µõ :
    {‚ä©A : Œì ‚ä©·µõ‚ü® l ‚ü© A / ‚ä©Œì}

    ‚àÄ u ‚Üí
